WEBVTT

00:07.120 --> 00:08.740
I will confess! I will!

00:09.200 --> 00:10.370
It's Second Young Master.

00:10.600 --> 00:12.260
He's been sending someone
to hunt me down

00:12.440 --> 00:13.580
because...

00:13.870 --> 00:15.610
Because of Mr. Anping.

00:17.920 --> 00:19.930
That day, at Drunken Bordello...

00:20.510 --> 00:21.650
Han.

00:21.830 --> 00:24.090
Han, look. Someone beat me.

00:24.310 --> 00:26.130
Call a few men to go with me
and avenge me.

00:26.190 --> 00:27.330
Let's go.

00:36.070 --> 00:37.210
You...

00:37.920 --> 00:39.900
Why?

00:58.960 --> 01:00.240
- Take care of it.
- Yes.

01:05.110 --> 01:06.900
I've failed you, Your Highness.

01:07.030 --> 01:09.050
I've failed Mr. Anping.

01:09.520 --> 01:11.719
I was terrified
of being hunted by him,

01:11.720 --> 01:14.940
so I had to hide among the refugees.

02:18.960 --> 02:20.340
You're frightening me.

02:21.870 --> 02:23.010
Where were you

02:24.320 --> 02:25.460
tonight?

02:28.710 --> 02:29.850
I...

02:30.200 --> 02:31.410
Do you know

02:31.920 --> 02:33.340
where I went

02:33.710 --> 02:34.970
and what I saw tonight?

02:39.520 --> 02:41.130
How am I supposed to know?

03:03.200 --> 03:04.780
I searched through the entire capital

03:05.520 --> 03:07.060
to find this necklace.

03:08.800 --> 03:11.540
Today is your first birthday

03:12.480 --> 03:13.730
after our wedding.

03:16.550 --> 03:18.060
I didn't know today

03:19.640 --> 03:21.570
was my birthday.

03:31.830 --> 03:32.989
When I saw this necklace,

03:32.990 --> 03:34.450
I thought it was perfect for you.

03:35.240 --> 03:36.380
Do you like it?

03:43.550 --> 03:44.690
I do.

03:51.360 --> 03:52.500
What's wrong?

03:54.920 --> 03:56.060
Did I

03:56.320 --> 03:58.010
do anything wrong again?

04:01.480 --> 04:02.620
No.

04:05.270 --> 04:06.410
It's because

04:09.830 --> 04:12.620
only Zhao celebrated my birthday
back then.

04:17.320 --> 04:18.460
From now on,

04:19.790 --> 04:21.280
I'll celebrate your birthday with you

04:22.270 --> 04:23.450
every year,

04:24.470 --> 04:25.610
all right?

04:29.830 --> 04:30.970
Sure.

04:38.230 --> 04:39.370
Muyu,

04:40.150 --> 04:41.770
is there anything

04:43.000 --> 04:44.500
you're hiding from me?

04:51.790 --> 04:53.380
I've done many things wrong

04:58.760 --> 05:00.570
and I've hurt you.

05:02.200 --> 05:03.820
If you could mend your ways,

05:07.520 --> 05:09.690
would you do it for me?

07:15.260 --> 07:19.419
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

07:19.420 --> 07:22.680
=Episode 33=

07:22.740 --> 07:28.120
(Natural Grace and Talent)

07:34.060 --> 07:36.080
Your Majesty,
you just regained your consciousness.

07:36.470 --> 07:38.530
Please take this pill.

07:41.710 --> 07:43.450
Where's Official Lu?

07:43.790 --> 07:46.770
Official Lu failed his duty and has
requested to return to his hometown.

07:47.150 --> 07:48.709
The Taoist I invited

07:48.710 --> 07:50.570
was recommended by him.

07:51.030 --> 07:53.079
Besides, Wang Yuan waits on you
day and night.

07:53.080 --> 07:55.060
You will recover soon.

07:55.640 --> 07:56.890
This is strange.

07:58.230 --> 08:03.210
Official Lu always advised me

08:03.230 --> 08:04.980
to quit taking pills and cultivation.

08:05.470 --> 08:07.620
Why would he recommend a Taoist?

08:09.080 --> 08:12.500
If Wang Yuan has been waiting on me,

08:13.760 --> 08:16.620
who's overseeing the Directorate
of the Credentials then?

08:17.270 --> 08:21.210
Was it Wang Ge?

08:22.680 --> 08:23.820
Your Majesty,

08:24.030 --> 08:26.349
please don't trouble yourself
with such trivial matters.

08:26.350 --> 08:28.060
Your health is important.

08:33.440 --> 08:37.260
Your smile reminds me

08:38.630 --> 08:41.650
of when you first entered the palace.

08:42.990 --> 08:44.580
Back then,

08:44.630 --> 08:48.740
we often stayed up all night
discussing state affairs.

08:49.590 --> 08:52.810
Sometimes, I would grow tired,

08:53.750 --> 08:55.740
but you were still all smiles.

08:57.560 --> 09:01.500
As bright as the morning sun.

09:05.590 --> 09:07.220
I was ignorant back then.

09:08.920 --> 09:12.340
I entrusted Youting to the late Empress

09:13.680 --> 09:16.130
and sent him over to his fief early.

09:17.110 --> 09:18.650
That's unfair to you.

09:19.800 --> 09:21.580
Speak freely

09:24.750 --> 09:27.130
if you have any resentment.

09:38.680 --> 09:39.679
Your Majesty,

09:39.680 --> 09:41.930
maybe you should rest for tonight.

09:41.960 --> 09:43.290
It's already midnight.

09:45.630 --> 09:47.860
His Majesty has been
feeling unwell recently.

09:48.200 --> 09:51.290
If I slack off and delay the operations
of the Six Departments,

09:51.400 --> 09:52.580
problems might arise.

09:54.230 --> 09:55.740
Has His Majesty retired for the night?

09:55.800 --> 09:56.940
Not yet.

09:57.110 --> 09:59.100
His Majesty is coughing severely.

10:04.420 --> 10:06.560
(Natural Grace and Talent)

10:10.020 --> 10:12.000
(Yuxi Palace)

10:14.320 --> 10:15.890
After my passing,

10:16.200 --> 10:18.220
this will be the last decree.

10:18.470 --> 10:20.220
The Empress is to be buried with me

10:20.800 --> 10:22.700
to prevent the harem's involvement
in politics.

10:31.440 --> 10:33.050
Before I entered the palace,

10:33.110 --> 10:34.740
I once disguised myself as a man

10:34.800 --> 10:36.620
to attend the imperial exam.

10:37.440 --> 10:39.629
My parents caught me

10:39.630 --> 10:41.100
and punished me.

10:42.550 --> 10:44.770
They said women should never
interfere in state affairs.

10:46.990 --> 10:48.650
But you never criticized me.

10:49.590 --> 10:51.770
Instead, you praised my talent,

10:52.320 --> 10:54.740
taught me how to manage state affairs,

10:54.920 --> 10:56.620
and rewarded me with countless honors.

10:57.680 --> 10:58.820
If someone has to be blamed,

10:59.440 --> 11:02.740
blame me for my greed for power
and overstepping my bounds.

11:07.560 --> 11:08.980
How could I ever do that?

11:10.680 --> 11:11.890
Over the years,

11:14.470 --> 11:16.220
I've been fortunate to have you.

11:17.870 --> 11:21.039
I'm truly grateful to you.

11:21.040 --> 11:23.770
I can't handle
all the internal and external affairs

11:23.990 --> 11:25.530
by myself.

11:26.400 --> 11:27.930
For the nation,

11:28.160 --> 11:29.930
please take this pill

11:30.280 --> 11:31.279
and recover soon.

11:31.280 --> 11:32.129
This is absurd.

11:32.130 --> 11:33.279
Father has just woken up.

11:33.280 --> 11:35.050
As his son, can't I even visit him?

11:38.920 --> 11:40.039
Your Majesty.

11:40.040 --> 11:41.340
Your Majesty,

11:41.400 --> 11:44.199
I couldn't stop the Crown Prince
and Official Liang.

11:44.200 --> 11:46.439
I accept any punishment.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.740
I may be your subject,

11:48.160 --> 11:49.580
but above all, I'm your son.

11:49.900 --> 11:51.410
You've finally awakened

11:51.920 --> 11:52.769
after so long.

11:52.770 --> 11:53.989
For any reason,

11:53.990 --> 11:56.040
I should stay with my own father.

11:56.790 --> 11:58.500
If you wish to punish me,

11:59.320 --> 12:00.500
I accept it.

12:01.400 --> 12:02.700
But if this ever happens again,

12:04.510 --> 12:06.340
I'd do the same.

12:12.040 --> 12:13.340
Youcheng,

12:16.200 --> 12:18.810
you've finally behaved like an heir.

12:26.750 --> 12:27.930
Official Liang,

12:28.590 --> 12:30.380
you risked your life to come here.

12:30.870 --> 12:32.580
State your urgent matter.

12:32.990 --> 12:35.460
What I wish to propose concerns

12:36.080 --> 12:37.959
about this year's
ancestral worship ceremony

12:37.960 --> 12:40.530
prepared by the Ministry of Rites.

12:40.990 --> 12:43.380
Given your frail condition,

12:43.410 --> 12:44.799
such a long journey is inadvisable.

12:44.800 --> 12:46.530
I'm deeply concerned.

12:46.800 --> 12:49.930
However, the ancestral worship ceremony
is of national significance.

12:50.230 --> 12:53.410
Therefore, I venture
to request your permission

12:55.170 --> 12:57.010
for the Crown Prince to attend
in your place.

13:01.040 --> 13:03.000
The rain appears

13:04.830 --> 13:07.000
as a godsend.

13:10.990 --> 13:12.130
Granted.

13:12.270 --> 13:13.410
Father,

13:13.470 --> 13:15.229
I should remain by your side

13:15.230 --> 13:16.399
to take care of you.

13:16.400 --> 13:17.940
The Crown Prince is indeed considerate.

13:18.160 --> 13:19.159
Perhaps the ceremony

13:19.160 --> 13:20.039
could be postponed.

13:20.040 --> 13:22.460
I have Official Liang
and the rest with me.

13:22.590 --> 13:24.170
No need to worry so much.

13:24.920 --> 13:28.170
This is a decree,

13:29.830 --> 13:31.220
not a negotiation.

13:33.320 --> 13:35.770
I accept your decree, Father.

13:35.830 --> 13:37.860
Wise decision, Your Majesty.

13:38.160 --> 13:40.500
Let Gu Yu tag along.

13:40.590 --> 13:43.030
He was just promoted to
Senior Commandant-in-Chief of Cavalry.

13:43.040 --> 13:44.589
He can lead some men

13:44.590 --> 13:46.100
to escort the Crown Prince.

13:46.520 --> 13:47.740
Consider it

13:47.920 --> 13:50.500
a small favor for my family

13:51.200 --> 13:53.410
and a convenience for him
to rise in rank later.

13:55.230 --> 13:57.410
Since you've said so,

13:59.160 --> 14:00.410
I'll grant my permission.

14:01.200 --> 14:04.260
I shall thank you on Gu Yu's behalf.

14:05.280 --> 14:08.050
His Majesty and Liang Jifang
put on quite a display

14:08.060 --> 14:10.180
to have the Crown Prince
lead the ancestral ceremony.

14:10.750 --> 14:14.050
It's obvious that they intend for him
to inherit the throne.

14:14.680 --> 14:16.620
I assign you to lead a troop
to the ceremony

14:16.630 --> 14:19.420
is to give you a chance to earn
the first merit under the new Emperor.

14:22.160 --> 14:23.300
Yu,

14:24.160 --> 14:26.130
I've treated you well all these years.

14:27.280 --> 14:28.890
It's time to grow up.

14:31.720 --> 14:33.170
I understand what you mean, Aunt.

14:34.040 --> 14:35.180
Aunt,

14:35.470 --> 14:37.700
could you please spare Yantang?

14:50.897 --> 14:52.860
If you accomplish
this task successfully,

14:53.350 --> 14:54.770
the new reign will be stable,

14:55.630 --> 14:58.170
and Song Mo won't have to die.

14:59.750 --> 15:01.050
Not just that,

15:02.200 --> 15:04.770
you can marry any woman you like

15:05.320 --> 15:07.010
and ask for any title you want.

15:07.580 --> 15:09.500
I will grant you all.

15:13.160 --> 15:14.340
Understood.

15:31.590 --> 15:34.319
Besides, for the sake of the nation,

15:34.320 --> 15:36.860
don't allow Youting to enter the capital
for the funeral.

15:36.880 --> 15:38.719
If Liaodong shows a sign
of unusual movement,

15:38.720 --> 15:40.410
secretly instruct the Duke of Ding

15:40.420 --> 15:42.820
to quell the chaos
under the name of suppressing rebellion.

15:44.800 --> 15:45.940
Your Majesty.

15:47.630 --> 15:49.170
From the very beginning,

15:49.680 --> 15:51.860
you all have been forcing me.

16:00.750 --> 16:03.810
Your archery skills are no longer
inferior to Song Mo's.

16:04.280 --> 16:05.580
On the fifteenth day,

16:06.080 --> 16:09.410
you will command all the troops
from Chengtian Gate to Zhiyang Gate.

16:10.080 --> 16:11.500
Once the time comes,

16:11.750 --> 16:13.220
open the Daming Gate.

16:13.470 --> 16:14.610
A coup?

16:14.750 --> 16:17.159
My head could roll.

16:17.160 --> 16:18.740
I need to get what I deserve.

16:19.400 --> 16:20.540
I'm not done yet.

16:21.040 --> 16:22.410
Your Princess Anyu

16:22.830 --> 16:25.220
grew up together with Dou Zhao.

16:26.080 --> 16:27.530
To achieve great things,

16:28.320 --> 16:30.129
you have to be ruthless,

16:30.130 --> 16:32.530
especially when you've
sought my refugee.

16:32.970 --> 16:35.210
Learn from your father's mistake.

16:36.370 --> 16:37.890
Among twenty-six units in the capital,

16:38.280 --> 16:40.700
apart from the Imperial Guard,

16:40.810 --> 16:42.349
for the rest who are in power

16:42.350 --> 16:44.410
to stay out of it on that day,

16:44.560 --> 16:47.860
just how much effort and money
it will take.

16:48.440 --> 16:49.980
Can you afford that, Your Highness?

16:50.320 --> 16:51.740
Without the Miao family,

16:52.750 --> 16:54.220
I can't do anything.

16:54.960 --> 16:56.869
It's fine if you don't want to kill her.

16:56.870 --> 16:58.810
I really disapprove

16:59.990 --> 17:02.260
of your tone.

17:02.650 --> 17:03.980
Whether you like it or not,

17:04.440 --> 17:05.580
I don't care.

17:09.710 --> 17:11.509
If you want
the entire Soaring Steed Guard

17:11.510 --> 17:12.900
to act according to your plan,

17:13.160 --> 17:14.370
you need to understand

17:14.510 --> 17:17.370
that it's not me
seeking refuge with you,

17:17.400 --> 17:21.090
it's you who needs me instead.

17:24.510 --> 17:25.980
I can kill you if I want.

17:38.030 --> 17:41.500
A dead man can't work with you.

17:41.680 --> 17:43.530
I need to obtain what I deserve.

17:43.790 --> 17:44.930
Very well.

17:46.160 --> 17:47.870
You have guts and spirits.

17:48.270 --> 17:50.180
My plan will definitely succeed.

17:51.920 --> 17:53.060
Come.

17:54.380 --> 17:56.989
(Map)

17:56.990 --> 17:59.530
Pick any land you want.

18:01.400 --> 18:03.900
You'll be the first non-royal lord
of the new reign.

18:06.790 --> 18:07.980
You're wise, Your Highness.

18:08.510 --> 18:10.330
I'll send her
out of the capital immediately

18:10.530 --> 18:12.740
so that you can rest assured.

18:32.360 --> 18:34.610
This hairpin fits you beautifully.

18:39.260 --> 18:42.309
Muyu, there's something
I want to discuss with you.

18:42.310 --> 18:43.450
What's it?

18:44.120 --> 18:46.050
Father and Mother have been upset.

18:46.070 --> 18:48.700
They want to take my brother's
memorial tablet back to our hometown

18:48.710 --> 18:50.660
and enshrine it at a temple
for praying.

18:50.880 --> 18:53.260
I'd like to accompany them to Futing.

18:56.240 --> 18:58.090
As long as you're back
after Lantern Festival.

18:58.400 --> 19:00.500
That's when every family
gathers together.

19:00.680 --> 19:01.980
I don't want you to be alone.

19:02.440 --> 19:04.090
If we're deeply in love,

19:04.770 --> 19:06.330
being apart for a few days is nothing.

19:06.800 --> 19:08.370
I don't want you to get tired

19:08.670 --> 19:09.810
from the journey.

19:10.440 --> 19:11.580
All right.

19:11.880 --> 19:13.020
As you say.

19:19.490 --> 19:20.630
Yantang.

19:22.440 --> 19:23.580
Yantang.

19:26.070 --> 19:27.260
Su Xin, Su Lan.

19:29.030 --> 19:29.879
Madam.

19:29.880 --> 19:30.769
Madam.

19:30.770 --> 19:32.010
Where's Yantang?

19:34.120 --> 19:36.290
Master loses all his senses
when the poison flares up

19:36.310 --> 19:38.639
and might accidentally hurt you.

19:38.640 --> 19:40.469
You can give him the medicine
when he's sober.

19:40.470 --> 19:41.979
His pulse shows a worsening sign.

19:41.980 --> 19:43.539
If he doesn't take the medicine,

19:43.540 --> 19:45.040
the poison could be beyond control.

19:45.170 --> 19:46.099
Uh...

19:46.100 --> 19:47.640
Tell me where he is now.

19:47.950 --> 19:50.360
Master locked himself in the bathhouse.

19:50.410 --> 19:51.950
He won't answer the door.

19:52.690 --> 19:53.830
Madam.

19:57.540 --> 19:58.419
Madam.

19:58.420 --> 19:59.560
- Madam.
- Madam.

20:06.220 --> 20:07.360
Yantang.

20:08.020 --> 20:09.160
Yantang.

20:11.850 --> 20:13.080
Yantang.

20:14.340 --> 20:15.179
Madam.

20:15.180 --> 20:17.160
Master has been inside for long.

20:20.580 --> 20:21.960
Leave us for now.

20:22.270 --> 20:23.480
- Yes, Madam.
- Yes, Madam.

20:23.900 --> 20:25.040
Yantang.

20:25.540 --> 20:26.619
Ms. Longevity,

20:26.620 --> 20:27.800
don't come in.

20:28.380 --> 20:29.600
I'm all right now.

20:29.980 --> 20:31.120
I just

20:31.980 --> 20:34.040
don't want you to see me now.

20:34.340 --> 20:35.640
You are my husband.

20:35.980 --> 20:38.800
Even if your hair turns all white,
I won't fear you either.

20:41.500 --> 20:42.800
Even so,

20:43.100 --> 20:46.339
I wish to leave a perfect image

20:46.340 --> 20:47.859
to you.

20:47.860 --> 20:49.000
Yantang,

20:49.220 --> 20:51.080
I've concocted a new remedy.

20:51.120 --> 20:52.699
It will slow down the poison inside you.

20:52.700 --> 20:53.819
Open the door now.

20:53.820 --> 20:56.760
The previous remedy took effect.

20:56.820 --> 20:58.040
Now I feel...

20:59.940 --> 21:01.080
Yantang.

21:05.980 --> 21:07.120
Yantang.

21:10.060 --> 21:12.240
Yantang.

21:12.740 --> 21:14.560
Here. Take the medicine.

21:29.980 --> 21:31.120
Yantang.

21:31.500 --> 21:34.800
I'm Ms. Longevity.

21:41.500 --> 21:42.640
Yantang.

21:43.820 --> 21:44.960
Yantang.

21:45.140 --> 21:46.139
Yantang.

21:46.140 --> 21:47.720
Yantang, wake up.

21:47.900 --> 21:49.760
Hurry and take the medicine.

21:49.980 --> 21:51.120
Ms. Longevity.

21:51.140 --> 21:52.760
I can't control myself right now.

21:53.620 --> 21:55.280
I might hurt you.

22:15.180 --> 22:16.840
(Rest in the Flow,
Clarity in the Stones)

22:20.180 --> 22:21.320
Yantang,

22:22.260 --> 22:24.480
we've long been bound as one.

22:34.540 --> 22:35.680
Ansu,

22:36.020 --> 22:37.200
read this on the way.

22:38.860 --> 22:40.939
(Shantong, Hanzhou, Yuzhou, Heguan,
Kangnan, Futing)

22:40.940 --> 22:43.080
Pick a place you like the most.

22:43.820 --> 22:44.960
Tell me later.

22:45.980 --> 22:47.320
What's this for?

22:57.500 --> 22:59.160
It wouldn't be a surprise if I tell.

23:00.300 --> 23:01.600
I'll write to you.

23:01.660 --> 23:04.000
Together with my good news.

23:20.180 --> 23:23.120
(Yongding Gate)

23:25.780 --> 23:26.859
(Rest in the Flow,
Clarity in the Stones)

23:26.860 --> 23:28.440
Do you remember

23:28.700 --> 23:31.160
the rainy night when we first met?

23:33.140 --> 23:35.760
Rainy rain, estate.

23:36.380 --> 23:38.560
You wanted to kill me

23:39.060 --> 23:40.779
when we first met.

23:40.780 --> 23:42.200
(Loyal)

23:42.460 --> 23:45.259
You were composed

23:45.260 --> 23:46.579
and calm.

23:46.580 --> 23:48.360
I almost lost my composure,

23:48.740 --> 23:50.760
but I pretended to stay calm

23:51.140 --> 23:53.640
so that the guards wouldn't notice.

23:54.090 --> 23:55.230
Really?

23:57.100 --> 24:00.019
I was truly anxious inside,

24:00.020 --> 24:01.560
but I kept pretending.

24:02.660 --> 24:06.139
Your eyes were aggressive.

24:06.140 --> 24:07.920
They could scare anyone away.

24:08.140 --> 24:09.710
But I felt

24:10.290 --> 24:13.800
as if we were friends for years.

24:14.950 --> 24:16.800
Aside from fear,

24:19.180 --> 24:21.080
your eyes showed anticipation.

24:22.580 --> 24:25.040
If I told you

24:25.470 --> 24:28.080
that I once dreamed

24:29.000 --> 24:32.610
of us experiencing life
and death together,

24:33.860 --> 24:35.240
would you believe me?

24:35.660 --> 24:36.800
I would.

24:37.420 --> 24:39.659
And I hope

24:39.660 --> 24:41.120
we can stay together

24:41.460 --> 24:42.960
in many lives to come.

24:43.500 --> 24:45.479
Don't be cheesy.

24:45.480 --> 24:48.080
You're turning my words into a joke.

24:49.260 --> 24:50.720
It's not a joke.

24:51.820 --> 24:54.920
I'm grateful for that rainy night

24:54.960 --> 24:56.440
for bringing you to me.

24:58.260 --> 24:59.880
When the magnolia blooms,

24:59.890 --> 25:01.579
let's travel to see
famous rivers and seas

25:01.580 --> 25:03.440
and admire spring bloom
and autumn moon.

25:03.500 --> 25:04.640
What do you say?

25:07.300 --> 25:08.520
There's no need to wait.

25:08.740 --> 25:11.560
You've already given me spring.

25:30.100 --> 25:34.579
(Diecui Pavilion)

25:34.580 --> 25:36.040
Madam, Master,

25:37.140 --> 25:39.200
Her Majesty's court lady came
with a decree.

25:42.060 --> 25:43.499
By Her Majesty's decree,

25:43.500 --> 25:45.800
you're invited
to the palace banquet, Madam.

27:00.260 --> 27:01.400
Your Highness.

27:03.540 --> 27:04.760
Earl of Yunyang,

27:05.500 --> 27:07.880
you're tight with Song Mo and his wife.

27:08.140 --> 27:12.040
I thought you would choose
the side of the greater cause.

27:12.620 --> 27:14.299
After all, she's my aunt.

27:14.300 --> 27:15.440
Blood is thicker than water.

27:16.580 --> 27:18.560
Also, I need to leave myself a way out.

27:19.460 --> 27:21.640
Your Highness, you have to stop here.

27:25.780 --> 27:28.080
(Melody of Bamboo and Pines)

27:28.600 --> 27:30.120
They actually fought?

27:33.120 --> 27:34.579
The Duke of Ying's poison flared up.

27:34.580 --> 27:37.480
They fought from the bathhouse
all the way outside and smashed everything.

27:37.540 --> 27:40.840
Their faces looked pale, their breathing
was rapid and their hands were trembling.

27:40.940 --> 27:42.579
But they don't seem to be injured.

27:42.580 --> 27:43.840
It's more like sick.

27:46.900 --> 27:48.080
Whether true or not,

27:48.140 --> 27:50.160
I'll explain this to His Highness.

27:51.700 --> 27:53.280
Keep a close watch on Yizhi Hall.

27:53.340 --> 27:55.640
Report to me once anything happens.

27:57.180 --> 27:58.320
Yes.

28:02.500 --> 28:04.440
Father has barely been awake,

28:05.900 --> 28:08.160
and everything has become complicated.

28:22.060 --> 28:23.720
Father refuses to take the pill,

28:24.300 --> 28:26.040
so Mother changes the incense

28:26.420 --> 28:28.600
to put Father to sleep.

28:28.980 --> 28:30.120
In case anything happens,

28:31.700 --> 28:34.680
no external officials are allowed
to enter Xihua Gate.

28:34.900 --> 28:37.360
Her Majesty merely relies on a Taoist.

28:37.620 --> 28:40.120
I'm afraid something could go wrong.

28:40.680 --> 28:42.760
I'd like to trouble you
by making a trip there, sir.

28:43.060 --> 28:44.440
Before the Lantern Festival,

28:45.300 --> 28:47.400
no mistakes can be afforded.

28:50.820 --> 28:52.760
If the Crown Prince returns now,

28:52.910 --> 28:54.259
he'll surely ascend to the throne.

28:54.260 --> 28:56.560
Song Mo and his wife are scheming.

28:57.100 --> 28:59.020
They pose a threat.

28:59.540 --> 29:01.840
A big threat, indeed.

29:04.833 --> 29:06.618
News from Shadow Guards reports

29:06.740 --> 29:09.440
that Dou Zhao and he had a fight
at Zhiyi Hall.

29:10.020 --> 29:11.459
The entire yard was in a mess.

29:11.460 --> 29:13.619
Song Mo is now too ill

29:13.620 --> 29:15.200
to care about court affairs.

29:16.860 --> 29:19.120
The coup is now or never.

29:22.780 --> 29:27.200
(Xuanyue Palace)

29:38.860 --> 29:40.720
What's the situation at Yuxi Palace?

29:41.620 --> 29:44.240
Lord Qing is concerned about it.

29:44.460 --> 29:46.539
He had Official Ji enter the palace

29:46.540 --> 29:49.320
to check His Majesty's pulse
and perform acupuncture.

29:49.860 --> 29:52.050
Those from the Imperial Medical Bureau
daren't disclose anything.

29:52.220 --> 29:53.960
But I have to be frank with you.

29:55.060 --> 29:56.780
If His Majesty's condition
doesn't improve,

29:57.170 --> 29:59.120
I'm afraid he won't last
until the next spring.

30:07.660 --> 30:08.800
All of them

30:09.540 --> 30:10.960
are ready.

30:26.900 --> 30:28.240
The Western craftmanship

30:29.780 --> 30:31.000
are indeed unique.

30:32.700 --> 30:34.800
Why hasn't the Duchess of Ying
shown up yet?

30:35.100 --> 30:36.219
A few concubines and I

30:36.220 --> 30:37.840
found a new business

30:38.220 --> 30:40.680
and are hoping to seek her advice.

30:41.020 --> 30:42.259
Madam Mu,

30:42.260 --> 30:43.960
you have to be cautious.

30:44.140 --> 30:45.779
Two women from the Dou family

30:45.780 --> 30:47.579
ruined my son

30:47.580 --> 30:49.859
and brought great harm
to the Duke of Ying's family.

30:49.860 --> 30:51.040
She's such a jinx.

30:52.340 --> 30:54.720
The Dou family is down and out now.

30:54.860 --> 30:56.499
She's to blame.

30:56.500 --> 30:59.480
I guess she's now riding
a mule carriage here.

31:00.300 --> 31:02.200
Madam Wei, don't look down on her.

31:02.570 --> 31:04.259
Can you guess who sent
these exotic gifts

31:04.260 --> 31:06.320
to Her Majesty?

31:06.500 --> 31:09.280
Don't tell me it's that jinxed woman.

31:10.380 --> 31:12.280
Looks like the donkey carriage
isn't that slow.

31:12.900 --> 31:14.259
But the donkey in the stable

31:14.260 --> 31:15.459
sure is loud.

31:15.460 --> 31:16.699
I can hear it from outside.

31:16.700 --> 31:17.880
Who are you calling a donkey?

31:17.890 --> 31:20.020
- Who's the donkey yelling at?
-The donkey is yelling at you.

31:22.820 --> 31:25.760
- You!
- Here comes Her Majesty.

31:29.300 --> 31:31.600
Greetings, Her Majesty.

31:33.900 --> 31:35.619
Greetings, Her Majesty.

31:35.620 --> 31:37.880
Greetings, Her Majesty.

31:38.700 --> 31:39.819
Tonight is a family banquet,

31:39.820 --> 31:41.280
so please do away with formalities.

31:42.100 --> 31:43.520
Please be seated.

31:56.660 --> 31:58.259
These exotic gifts

31:58.260 --> 32:00.520
intrigue me.

32:00.540 --> 32:01.800
Speaking of which,

32:02.020 --> 32:04.360
the Duchess of Ying is so thoughtful.

32:04.540 --> 32:06.480
It's really the Duchess of Ying.

32:06.540 --> 32:07.899
I heard she also

32:07.900 --> 32:09.840
prepared a unique performance.

32:35.660 --> 32:36.960
What a beautiful dance.

32:56.780 --> 32:58.600
These ladies are dancing so excellently.

32:58.980 --> 33:00.320
They are all talents.

33:00.660 --> 33:01.960
Not really.

33:02.060 --> 33:03.620
They just each have their own interest.

33:03.860 --> 33:05.659
They acquired those skills
to make a living

33:05.660 --> 33:06.899
and not rely on their families

33:06.900 --> 33:08.240
or men.

33:22.280 --> 33:24.600
We've been awaiting you, Your Highness.

33:24.820 --> 33:27.120
Take Qianqing Palace down
as quickly as possible.

33:27.820 --> 33:29.080
Once the sky brightens,

33:29.100 --> 33:31.520
I'm going to hold the imperial seal
and command the country.

33:31.860 --> 33:33.000
Tonight,

33:33.720 --> 33:35.660
we'll eradicate bad influences
around the Emperor

33:35.740 --> 33:37.160
and reestablish the court.

33:41.580 --> 33:42.579
Bravo!

33:42.580 --> 33:44.600
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

33:58.180 --> 33:59.619
I've prepared

33:59.620 --> 34:01.280
a century-old floral brew for you.

34:01.820 --> 34:03.360
Allow me to make a wish.

34:03.740 --> 34:05.259
From this day forward,

34:05.260 --> 34:06.800
this land

34:06.880 --> 34:08.800
will usher in new changes.

34:25.740 --> 34:27.080
What does this mean?

34:27.180 --> 34:29.440
There are rebels emerging
in the palace tonight.

34:29.700 --> 34:32.200
Lord Qing is currently eliminating them.

34:32.580 --> 34:35.419
For your safety,

34:35.420 --> 34:38.640
Xuanyue Hall has to be sealed.

34:51.740 --> 34:52.880
Dou Zhao,

34:53.900 --> 34:55.040
stop waiting.

34:55.540 --> 34:57.080
No one is coming to your aid.

34:57.780 --> 34:58.920
Of course.

35:00.060 --> 35:01.139
So you've known all along

35:01.140 --> 35:03.680
that I'd take action
against the ladies tonight.

35:03.900 --> 35:06.720
You used the harem
to control the Imperial Medical Bureau

35:07.220 --> 35:08.899
and to keep His Majesty bedridden

35:08.900 --> 35:10.200
so that he's unable to govern.

35:10.420 --> 35:11.779
All you've been waiting for

35:11.780 --> 35:14.280
is to join hands with Lord Qing tonight.

35:16.220 --> 35:17.899
And Eunuch Wang
can falsely accuse anyone

35:17.900 --> 35:19.560
of being a rebel,

35:19.570 --> 35:20.419
for instance,

35:20.420 --> 35:23.480
Wang Yuan, the godfather
he has served for years.

35:24.340 --> 35:25.299
Hence, Lord Qing's men

35:25.300 --> 35:27.640
have a rightful reason
to eliminate other officials.

35:28.180 --> 35:29.899
You've confined us womenfolk

35:29.900 --> 35:31.640
in Xuanyue Hall.

35:31.740 --> 35:34.160
Naturally, the external court officials
will be restrained.

35:34.340 --> 35:36.859
Not only can Lord Qing enter
the palace unopposed,

35:36.860 --> 35:38.490
but he will also earn praise

35:38.500 --> 35:40.920
for quelling treason
and protecting the Emperor tomorrow.

35:41.740 --> 35:44.600
By then,
whether His Majesty lives or dies,

35:44.860 --> 35:46.160
the throne

35:46.300 --> 35:48.880
will fall into Lord Qing's hands.

35:51.540 --> 35:52.659
What should we do now?

35:52.660 --> 35:54.360
Are they committing treason?

35:58.820 --> 35:59.699
Dou Zhao,

35:59.700 --> 36:00.819
you're insane.

36:00.820 --> 36:02.160
Aren't you afraid of being killed?

36:03.100 --> 36:05.000
Don't panic, madams.

36:05.780 --> 36:08.720
Her Majesty only holds us as hostages.

36:08.740 --> 36:10.360
She won't harm our lives.

36:10.820 --> 36:12.520
If something were to happen to us,

36:13.060 --> 36:14.960
the officials wouldn't
let Lord Qing rest easy,

36:15.260 --> 36:17.600
not even if he ascended to the throne.

36:21.420 --> 36:23.320
I don't mind killing one or two.

36:24.380 --> 36:25.520
Dou Zhao,

36:25.780 --> 36:27.440
I'll start with you.

36:34.580 --> 36:35.720
Don't move.

36:35.900 --> 36:37.200
Su Yan, you...

36:37.420 --> 36:39.480
Madams, run now.

36:39.620 --> 36:40.859
Now!

36:40.860 --> 36:41.979
Stay still.

36:41.980 --> 36:44.000
Whoever defies me,
their families will be executed.

36:48.300 --> 36:50.000
Protect Her Majesty. Hurry!

36:52.860 --> 36:54.000
Stay still.

36:54.540 --> 36:56.120
If you come any close, I'll kill her.

36:57.820 --> 36:59.440
You prepared those lanterns.

36:59.660 --> 37:01.640
Your hands have even reached
the Ministry of Work.

37:01.680 --> 37:03.840
When you summoned me to the palace
to hold me hostage,

37:04.060 --> 37:05.280
did it never occur to you

37:05.300 --> 37:06.779
that I might fight back?

37:06.780 --> 37:07.859
Don't come near.

37:07.860 --> 37:09.000
Move.

37:12.820 --> 37:13.960
Quick.

37:17.340 --> 37:18.480
Stay back.

37:22.540 --> 37:23.680
Surrender.

37:23.900 --> 37:25.440
It's pointless for you to do this.

37:26.060 --> 37:27.200
Without Song Mo,

37:27.420 --> 37:29.160
what change can you make?

37:31.660 --> 37:32.800
Song Mo?

37:35.700 --> 37:36.840
Su Yan.

37:38.020 --> 37:39.200
Dou Zhao, run!

37:39.580 --> 37:40.699
Now!

37:40.700 --> 37:42.760
Protect my mother and brother.

37:42.820 --> 37:43.960
Go now!

37:56.900 --> 37:58.200
Surrender peacefully.

37:58.260 --> 37:59.920
You won't escape.

38:08.420 --> 38:10.200
Madam!

38:10.460 --> 38:11.960
- Madam!
- You're here.

38:12.420 --> 38:14.200
Madam, Lord Qing led a large troop

38:14.300 --> 38:15.920
and breached the Shuntian Gate.

38:25.820 --> 38:27.800
You came all the way to meet your death.

38:27.900 --> 38:29.040
Very well.

38:29.180 --> 38:30.320
Today,

38:30.420 --> 38:34.240
I'll send you all to meet Jiang Meisun.

38:34.420 --> 38:35.739
- Guards!
- Yes.

38:35.740 --> 38:39.200
Execute impertinent assassins

38:39.540 --> 38:40.920
immediately.

38:54.340 --> 38:55.560
Chen Jia, are you rebelling?

38:55.570 --> 38:57.139
I've wanted to kill him for a long time.

38:57.140 --> 38:59.320
Kill me if you want credits.

38:59.340 --> 39:00.339
You!

39:00.340 --> 39:01.880
Who's rebelling tonight?

39:02.420 --> 39:04.160
Haven't you figured it out yet?

39:04.620 --> 39:07.240
Wang Ge colluded with Lord Qing
to usurp the throne.

39:07.300 --> 39:10.040
To whom do the Shadow Guards
pledge their loyalty,

39:10.420 --> 39:12.120
the Emperor or the traitor?

39:12.300 --> 39:13.480
This is impossible.

39:14.220 --> 39:16.800
Don't listen to this madwoman.

39:18.780 --> 39:19.920
Men,

39:20.500 --> 39:23.360
the people see us as eunuch's lackeys,

39:24.140 --> 39:25.419
and those dignitaries treat us

39:25.420 --> 39:27.219
as killing tools and scapegoats.

39:27.220 --> 39:29.000
Haven't you had enough?

39:29.900 --> 39:31.400
I've had enough of all this!

39:38.000 --> 39:39.240
- Officer Chen.
- Officer Chen.

39:39.260 --> 39:40.840
- We'll follow you.
- We'll follow you.

39:43.180 --> 39:45.680
You all could tell right from wrong
and stand up for justice.

39:46.300 --> 39:47.960
His Majesty will reward you.

39:48.260 --> 39:51.000
If the evil really gains power tonight,

39:51.260 --> 39:52.400
I, Dou Zhao,

39:52.420 --> 39:54.200
will take all the blame.

39:54.540 --> 39:55.680
Chen Jia,

39:55.900 --> 39:58.280
Zhao Liangbi and you
will take the remaining Shadow Guards

39:58.420 --> 39:59.859
and those from Zhaowen Bookstore

39:59.860 --> 40:01.200
to guard the Chengtian Gate

40:01.260 --> 40:02.539
to stop Lord Qing and Song Han.

40:02.540 --> 40:03.419
Yes.

40:03.420 --> 40:04.560
Yes.

40:05.820 --> 40:08.040
To repay the ruler's grace and favor,

40:08.220 --> 40:11.040
I'm willing to wield my sword
to defend the Emperor to death!

40:11.140 --> 40:12.720
To defend the Emperor to death!

40:30.340 --> 40:31.600
He's here.

40:52.980 --> 40:54.539
Bring the token of the Ding Army along.

40:54.540 --> 40:55.680
Before the Lantern Festival,

40:55.900 --> 40:58.560
secretly command all Ding Army
to enter the capital by boat.

40:59.380 --> 41:00.560
Song Mo?

41:00.580 --> 41:02.120
Isn't he poisoned?

41:02.420 --> 41:04.200
This mere Ding Army

41:04.460 --> 41:06.480
is trying to turn the table?

41:06.780 --> 41:07.739
In your dreams!

41:07.740 --> 41:09.419
Ding Army, hear my command!

41:09.420 --> 41:10.560
At your service!

41:11.700 --> 41:13.200
Avenge

41:14.020 --> 41:15.419
the Marshal!

41:15.420 --> 41:22.539
Kill!

41:22.540 --> 41:28.440
Kill!

42:08.980 --> 42:10.120
Release.

42:13.020 --> 42:14.640
- Formations.
- Yes.

42:20.100 --> 42:21.019
Master,

42:21.020 --> 42:22.160
we've arrived.

42:24.700 --> 42:26.200
Wang Ge can't be trusted anymore.

42:26.540 --> 42:27.720
Mother...

42:28.620 --> 42:30.080
- Guards!
- Yes.

42:30.500 --> 42:31.739
Deploy all the reserve troops!

42:31.740 --> 42:32.880
Yes.

42:33.700 --> 42:34.880
They outnumber us,

42:35.300 --> 42:36.379
but don't panic.

42:36.380 --> 42:37.610
We'll fight and retreat slowly.

42:40.860 --> 42:42.680
Kill!

42:50.300 --> 42:51.520
A fish in a barrel.

43:07.610 --> 43:08.539
His Majesty

43:08.540 --> 43:10.600
is sinking fast.

43:11.100 --> 43:13.779
Quell the rebels and protect the nation!

43:13.780 --> 43:16.219
It's now or never.

43:16.220 --> 43:18.840
Charge!

43:19.360 --> 43:21.989
♪The lingering uncertainty
has yet been resolved♪

43:21.990 --> 43:26.469
♪I gaze at you, and all is calm♪

43:26.470 --> 43:30.230
♪The world is vast and turbulent♪

43:30.390 --> 43:34.780
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:34.960 --> 43:38.889
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:38.890 --> 43:41.869
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

43:41.870 --> 43:44.079
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

43:44.080 --> 43:46.640
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

43:46.690 --> 43:50.260
♪Your presence
my side is irreplaceable♪

43:50.320 --> 43:53.840
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

43:53.850 --> 43:57.829
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

43:57.830 --> 44:01.860
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:02.300 --> 44:05.760
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:05.920 --> 44:08.100
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:08.120 --> 44:11.950
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:12.280 --> 44:15.420
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:15.960 --> 44:19.370
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:19.810 --> 44:23.350
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:23.550 --> 44:27.219
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:27.220 --> 44:31.560
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:31.620 --> 44:35.349
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:35.350 --> 44:38.829
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:38.830 --> 44:43.510
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

44:43.540 --> 44:47.129
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

44:47.130 --> 44:51.270
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

44:51.340 --> 44:54.630
♪Always together, looking back♪

44:54.940 --> 45:02.240
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:11.460 --> 45:12.419
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:12.420 --> 45:13.459
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:13.460 --> 45:14.680
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
